title: Seychelles Core Consumer Prices
description: Core Consumer Prices in Seychelles increased to 128.86 points in October from 128.38 points in September of 2022. Core Consumer Prices in Seychelles averaged 115 points from 2015 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 129.01 points in July of 2022 and a record low of 106.45 points in May of 2016. This page provides - Seychelles Core Consumer Prices- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Bureau of Statistics, Seychelles
